{"tid":1173426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山西躁漢搭唔到巴士 用西瓜打暈司機報復","createTime":"2019-05-27T06:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T08:58:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"859978a4f25c5f2b7e503b88e7f7f478d00f810f","tid":1173426,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190527/_2019052711465276301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190527%2F_2019052711465276301.jpg&h=d1e276ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，山西文水巴士司機被西瓜砸暈的影片引發關注。據了解，事發在本月19日，一名男子因未能上巴士，便搭乘的士追上巴士，攔停後上車用西瓜猛砸司機頭部。巴士司機說，對方有幾拳打在太陽穴上。司機還說，事後查看閉路電視，沒發現他揚手截車的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事情發生在5月19日的山西文水。巴士司機駕駛巴士正在路上行駛，忽然前面來了一輛的士攔車，於是巴士司機將車停下打開車門，一名男子從的士下來，然後飛快地跑上巴士將手中的西瓜砸向司機。司機緊急將車停下，拉好手剎，向自己的領導反映此事，同時報了警。然而，就在等待警察到來的過程中，這名男子再次揮起拳頭打向司機的太陽穴，導致其當場暈倒。現場，西瓜碎了一地，十分狼藉，司機暈倒在軚盤上，一動不動，該名男子還在罵不停。<br />\n<br />\n據現場乘客說，這名男子之所以這麼憤怒來毆打司機，是因為上不了巴士，然後就打的士追上巴士然後報復。但是，翻看閉路電視，根本沒有發現這名男子要搭車。目前，打人的男子已經被警察帶走調查。網民一致評論說：「關上幾個月就老實了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1009096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1009096&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWLuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=1f034632\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1009096&h=a70b6775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1009096</a>"},{"pid":"1d424661c2d54dc2f688172d3334c894ff550cf1","tid":1173426,"uid":17765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"禮儀之邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad44892f35e61a4fe2b9e97d350a9d132002856","tid":1173426,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"你唔停點知人地上唔上<br />\n飛站仲好意思出聲？"},{"pid":"0e1a124434407b500378cc95f6cbbed65491fdc8","tid":1173426,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"暈左咪又係冇車搭"},{"pid":"57487cf1d9562ac7c8be3d0cc1bd310232f6fe87","tid":1173426,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"飛站抵撚死啦"},{"pid":"eac4348159393e16a69c8b20bdb4e172682df29e","tid":1173426,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"條友唔係買榴槤你要還神喇"},{"pid":"beeb65fa1b04f6b9e8b1d427f2c8fd90b4a87c9f","tid":1173426,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97c6ee8e5c8ab7dcabd10cca4ae22e6da6684f","tid":1173426,"uid":196329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"你有咩問題"},{"pid":"105d4be4c82c00fc69d054e18f14b3392c655900","tid":1173426,"uid":170942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:42:16.000Z","msg":"以為用豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6d1f4ac776d48b9175df1c31fcd45adef4af44","tid":1173426,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c97c6ee8e5c8ab7dcabd10cca4ae22e6da6684f","tid":1173426,"uid":196329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:33:41.000Z","msg